Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Approved
body: On April 27, 2021, we approved your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190102995. We sent you an approval notice. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your approval notice by May 12, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Delivered To Me By The Post Office
body: On April 24, 2021, the Post Office delivered your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190102996, to the address that you gave us. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708405799781. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
